el. We also show that\n$h^\\mathrm{ann}_c(\\beta\\alpha)<h^\\mathrm{que}_c\n(\\beta)<h^\\mathrm{ann}_c(\\beta)$ for all $\\beta>0$ when $\\alpha>1$. This gap\nvanished when $\\alpha=1$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Oct 2011 16:41:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Feb 2012 21:55:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-02-21"}
